query:
SELECT p.productId, p.name, c.name as category_name
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
LEFT JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE p.brand = 'Thermo Fisher' AND p.name LIKE '%TG-%'
LIMIT 15;
